{"tid":1412230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有一些熱心醫護人員聯絡鄭松泰，希望可以提供義務醫療協助。","createTime":"2019-08-05T05:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:12:53.000Z","uid":107060,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2f7d0180d2cf2a0b42b66f1aabfc5af3c4b901a5","tid":1412230,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:52:49.000Z","msg":"#熱血義診<br />\n<br />\n由7月底起，特別是國務院記招正式宣告香港進入「警察政府」後，警方使用的暴力及武器鎮壓越趨嚴重，有示威者接連吸入催淚煙患上呼吸道問題，甚至有議員表示肺部感到不適。<br />\n<br />\n有一些熱心醫護人員聯絡本人，希望可以提供義務醫療協助，分別有：<br />\n<br />\n1. 中醫診治（中醫師特別強調，累積吸入催淚煙，需要中醫調理幫助排毒，從中醫角度，這才能治本，不用登記及記錄）<br />\n<br />\n2. 物理治療（物理治療師表示，受傷的義士（主要是關節受傷）可以尋求協助，亦備有便攜的治療器材可供外展使用；主治筋骨傷、甩骱、撞傷，識做都做，不用登記及記錄）<br />\n<br />\n3. 西醫門診<br />\n<br />\n4. 心理輔導（精神科專科）<br />\n<br />\n如有需要，請與天水圍逸澤社區主任黃頴思（電話：9547-5825）聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾人平安。<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰"},{"pid":"00c532bc60bc26883d9312944c4e60d46c5b929d","tid":1412230,"uid":107060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><del></del>"},{"pid":"8e28199971052b04b05b446a9f8b1f3678f233aa","tid":1412230,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848a1268cee849be4c0da3e1a9beb80d759cb7a0","tid":1412230,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f21a714c5bb5d4adaefc4a53828e4e1d29ed708","tid":1412230,"uid":266547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0a20902c71b888b6884d3166952ea4f7dba507","tid":1412230,"uid":33908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾多啲天水圍友知."},{"pid":"e1d77abaeaa0b6fc27977974353e8ba368fcff7a","tid":1412230,"uid":266547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6c163d05796aa145f2370bbb4cbc3074bbda09","tid":1412230,"uid":270307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:03:56.000Z","msg":"推 天水圍手足有需要就去"},{"pid":"ec496e917e3ebf2ccac2a46c124d7ceb7eb3e68a","tid":1412230,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:08:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f7c26eaa0f764e7df8ee65ac759e0569b628051","tid":1412230,"uid":3204,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:10:29.000Z","msg":"熱狗收皮"},{"pid":"a8e58982acf9106ebd053907222b9e24a2e8a3a1","tid":1412230,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}